19 1. Basic first aid training through the American Red Cross
20 or through a program with equivalent standards; and
21 2. Cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) training through
22 the American Heart Association or through a program with equivalent standards
23 appropriate for the ages of children for whom care is provided in the child care center; and
